    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Rise and shine! Before you begin\u2026</strong></p><p>Skim through these steps and get all your equipment ready, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Once done, simply dig in or wrap up ready for your day!</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/apple-and-cherry-cheesecake-pancakes/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>apple[s]</strong> into wedges (no need to peel!) and remove the core</p><p>Slice the <strong>wedges</strong>, then chop into small, bite-sized pieces</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/apple-and-cherry-cheesecake-pancakes/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Heat a small pot over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped apple </strong>to the pot with 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[65ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[85ml] </span><strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Cook for 6-7 min or until the apple has softened but still holding its shape (add another splash of water if it's looking a little dry!)</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/apple-and-cherry-cheesecake-pancakes/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>While the apple is cooking, combine 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[65ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[85ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>and mix until dissolved</p><p>Once dissolved, add your <strong>clotted cream</strong> and <strong>soft cheese</strong> and whisk until smooth and thick \u2013 this is your <strong>cheesecake filling</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/apple-and-cherry-cheesecake-pancakes/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>granola </strong>and <strong>ground</strong> <strong>cinnamon </strong>in a <strong>food processor</strong>, then blitz until you get a crumble texture \u2013 this is your <strong>granola cinnamon</strong> <strong>crumble</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/apple-and-cherry-cheesecake-pancakes/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the apples are cooked, add <strong>half</strong> your <strong>cherry sauce</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>apple & cherry topping</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/apple-and-cherry-cheesecake-pancakes/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once everything is ready, add your <strong>buttermilk pancakes</strong> to a plate and pop in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 30 secs on high or until warmed through</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/apple-and-cherry-cheesecake-pancakes/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Load the <strong>pancakes </strong>with the <strong>cheesecake filling</strong>, then top with the<strong> granola cinnamon</strong> <strong>crumble </strong>and the <strong>apple & cherry topping</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>remaining cherry sauce</strong> in a heart shape</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
